Series NCJ2 miniature cylinders available in spring return, spring extend, or double acting all offer stainless steel tubing and stainless steel rods.  Available in bore sizes 6, 10, 16mm and standard stroke lengths up to 8&quot;.  Basic, foot, front flange and double rear clevis mounting options.  Auto-switch capable.  Other features include non-rotating, double rod, rubber bumpers and a stainless steel body.
